      "asbval:evidence_quote": "SIRIUS 4 is written in Java; is open source under the GNU General Public License (version 3)... SIRIUS 4 integrates high-resolution isotope pattern analysis and fragmentation trees with structural elucidation to provide a combined and coherent assessment of molecular structures from MS/MS data for large datasets.",
      "asbval:note": "Paper confirms SIRIUS is Java-based and performs fragmentation tree computation, molecular formula deduction, and integration of downstream tools.",
