    {
      "@id": "asbval:assertion/skill/workflow-reconstruction/000",
      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "SIRIUS 4 integrates high-resolution isotope pattern analysis and fragmentation trees with structural elucidation to provide a combined and coherent assessment of molecular structures from MS/MS data for large datasets... SIRIUS 4 provides an intuitive graphical user interface... Extensive algorithm engineering and parallelization through a job-scheduling system... have reduced SIRIUS 4 running times by more than two orders of magnitude",
      "asbval:note": "Paper describes detailed computational workflow with tool integration, parameters, and decision logic for MS/MS analysis.",
